Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
reportDeCap(25.10)                                          reportDeCap(25.10)

Name
       reportDeCap - Reports placed decoupling capacitance cells in the speci-
       fied area

Syntax
       reportDeCap

       [-help]

       -area <x1 y1 x2 y2>

       Reports placed decoupling capacitance cells in the specified area.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs  a  brief description that includes type and default in-
              formation for each reportDeCap parameter.  For  a  detailed  de-
              scription  of the command and all of its parameters, use the man
              command: man reportDeCap.

       -area <x1 y1 x2 y2>
              Defines the area for which to report placed  decoupling  capaci-
              tance cells.

Example
       The  following  command  reports placed decoupling capacitance cells in
       the specified area:

       reportDeCap -area 250 250 1000 1000

